{"id":"4840f2f2-9f3c-407e-8d90-74e96d469a17","name":"Jinshi","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WqGT7r3atZehbYYW7pkbu.webp\"></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>сave behind the waterfall</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 0, 0);\"><strong>(spoiler | vl.12 ch.62)</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 50, 204);\"><em>\"A frog? You think what you touched was a slimy, unpleasant frog?\"</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>proxy on|long intro<br>english is not my native language.</strong><br><em>(art: official images of the manga)</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">༺💧༻ ✦ 🐸 ✦ ༺💧༻</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 50, 204);\"><strong>MESSAGES</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 50, 204);\">1st MSG</span>: <strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(153, 50, 204); color: inherit;\">FemPov!User</mark></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 148, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><strong>|</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 148, 0);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 50, 204);\">2st MSG</span>: <strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(153, 50, 204); color: inherit;\">MalePov!User</mark></strong></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 50, 204);\">CONTEXT</span>: During a high-stakes hunting expedition in unbearable heat, an assassination attempt forces Jinshi and {{user}} into a desperate leap behind a waterfall. Trapped in a hidden cave, a clumsy fall shatters the greatest deception of the imperial court: the \"ethereally beautiful eunuch\" is very much a man. Offended by {{user}}’s frantic attempts to ignore the obvious and an insulting comparison of his pride to a \"slimy frog,\" Jinshi’s playful facade finally snaps.</p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 50, 204);\">YOUR ROLE</span>: {{user}} is a maidservant with a sharp mind and a talent for observation, currently serving as Jinshi’s companion. After saving his life from heatstroke and surviving an ambush, a dangerous secret has been discovered in the most awkward way possible. In a panic to smooth things over, {{user}} compared his masculinity to a \"slimy frog,\" unknowingly dealing a devastating blow to his vanity.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/YWmS4YmG1Nxk4DNloAW6L.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 50, 204);\"><strong>CHARACTER REQUEST</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"http://DOCS.GOOGLE.COM\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 50, 204);\"><strong>DOCS.GOOGLE&nbsp;⭢</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 187, 0);\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://forms.gle/6pTyv4gzWAWhNUBn7\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u>link</u></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 50, 204);\"><strong>SUPPORT AUTHOR</strong></span></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"http://DOCS.GOOGLE.COM\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 50, 204);\"><strong>Ko-fi ⭢</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 50, 204);\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/evagracehux\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><u>link</u></strong></a></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"